### 3.7 Admin Dashboard Authentication (as of v3.1)

Basic Auth middleware is implemented in `src/index.js`. It activates only when both `ADMIN_USER` and `ADMIN_PASS` Railway env vars are set.

**Protected:** All `/api/` routes, `/newsletter-management`, `/admin`, `/dashboard`.

**Public (no auth required):** `/health`, `/api/confirm`, `/api/unsubscribe`, `/api/pause`, `POST /api/subscribers` (public signup form).

If `ADMIN_USER`/`ADMIN_PASS` are not set, the system fails open with a console warning. **Set these env vars before any public exposure of the Railway URL.**

